          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保斟酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，您前后喝了五碗啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒家！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（折桂令） 却不道五斗消醒，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三杯合道自有神功。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松饮酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斟上！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，您怎么还喝呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斟上！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保斟酒。武松饮酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（折桂令） 何用恁虚担惊恐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松抢坛子，抱坛痛饮。酒保见酒自坛口洒在地上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，糟蹋啦，糟蹋啦！可惜了的，可惜了的！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保急用嘴接酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这酒真好，是厉害！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒家，酒钱多少？"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四钱六分七厘八毫三。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒钱在此。“三碗不过岗”，俺吃了一坛，你看俺过得去岗过不去岗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，您上哪儿去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "景阳岗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "您真过景阳岗，那可不行。岗上出了一只吊睛白额大老虎，伤人甚众。您要过"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岗不是白白的送死吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不提猛虎，俺倒可不去；如今，你道岗上出了猛虎，俺是偏要过岗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去不得，您这不是给老虎送点心去吗！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （折桂令） 分明无事生风，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依仗口巧舌能；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休看俺醉眼朦胧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去不得，去不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松甩脱酒保，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去不得，哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保酒上涌，呕吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "酒保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（酒保抱酒坛，醉步蹒跚下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
