    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众猎户",
        "武松",
        "猎户甲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （沽美酒） 道崎岖，路不平，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只觉得站立不稳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿！酒家言道，这景阳岗上出了猛虎。分明是大话欺人，俺武松岂能受他的摆"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "布！待俺趱路。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松呕吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔……酒气上涌。那旁有一大石，待俺打睡片刻，有何不可！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松假寐，虎上，武松醒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！好大风，好大风！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松见虎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（雁儿落） 觑着这泼毛团体势雄，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狼牙棒先摧迸；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这孽畜舞爪张牙横。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（得胜令） 呀！哦呵闪——闪得它回身处扑着空，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转眼处乱着踪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狭路上冤家对面逢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（得胜令） 你要显神通，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管教你拳下尸骨横，拳下尸骨横。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "死了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松喘息。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待俺下岗趱路。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二猎户扮假虎同上，武松见虎欲打。众猎户急同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众猎户",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松呕吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔……"
        },
        {
          "character": "众猎户",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃行路的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众猎户",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这猛虎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "被俺打死了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众猎户",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀，这样一只大虫竟被你打死，真乃英雄也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夸奖了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问壮士尊姓大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下武松。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众猎户",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀，原来是武壮士。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就请壮士随我等一同回去，教大家看看你这打虎的英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就不敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众猎户",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "壮士请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众猎户同抬死虎，同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众猎户 （同沽美酒） 孽畜凶暴，路人惊恐，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多少人丧生含痛！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天降下打虎英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （沽美酒） 教众口将咱称颂，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无意中做了个打虎的英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众猎户 （同沽美酒） 也非是肆唇舌称颂，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在你那拳下尸横。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
